import React from 'react'
import { Flex, Text, Button, HStack, Box } from '@chakra-ui/core'
import { MdBookmarkBorder, MdControlPoint } from 'react-icons/md'
import {BsClipboardData} from 'react-icons/bs'

export const Header = () => {
  return (
    <Box d="flex" justifyContent="space-between" flexWrap="nowrap" minW="992px" maxW="1200px" w="100%" mx="auto" px="20px">
      <HStack mx="10">
        <Text>探索</Text>
        <Text>题库</Text>
        <Text>讨论</Text>
        <Text>竞赛</Text>
        <Text>企业</Text>
      </HStack>
      <HStack>
        <Button size="sm" leftIcon={<MdBookmarkBorder />} colorScheme="teal" variant="outline">下载App</Button>
        <Button size="sm" leftIcon={<MdControlPoint />} colorScheme="yellow" variant="outline">Plus会员</Button>
        <BsClipboardData />
      </HStack>      
    </Box>
  )
}
